Pat Woodell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Woodell 0 Patricia Joy Woodell (July 12, 1944 – September 29, 2015) was an American actress and singer, best known for her television role as Bobbie Jo Bradley from 1963 to 1965 on Petticoat Junction.
